    {
      "id": "quote:972eab96fc5513c7",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "So most of our listeners have probably heard by now that late last week, there was an attempted attack on Sam Altman at his house in San Francisco.",
        "episode_id": "25d702f6-ed6a-4565-8065-e729eb0f2650",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 3585,
        "char_end": 3732,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 221479,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 231320,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0001 - A.I. Backlash Turns Violent _ Ka_20260421-175353_8eb5f9d2.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:fbaa9271a9bf5eb3",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Yeah, so in that incident, an Indianapolis city councilman named Ron Gibson and his son woke up to more than a dozen gunshots being fired at their front door and a note tucked under their doormat that read, no data centers.",
        "episode_id": "25d702f6-ed6a-4565-8065-e729eb0f2650",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 4513,
        "char_end": 4736,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 286000,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 300839,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0001 - A.I. Backlash Turns Violent _ Ka_20260421-175353_8eb5f9d2.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:66afd1e0ec1b4042",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "And I think this is just part of what I am worried is a growing trend of anti-AI radicalization and violence.",
        "episode_id": "25d702f6-ed6a-4565-8065-e729eb0f2650",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 4899,
        "char_end": 5008,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 310720,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 320079,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0001 - A.I. Backlash Turns Violent _ Ka_20260421-175353_8eb5f9d2.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:e210c831a9518ce7",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "We'll debate what's making it so unpopular.",
        "episode_id": "25d702f6-ed6a-4565-8065-e729eb0f2650",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "claim",
        "position_hint": 0.04
      },
