    },
    {
      "id": "quote:1e2dbb0a79ec5bb1",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "This week, the AI backlash has turned violent. We'll debate what's making it so unpopular.",
        "episode_id": "25d702f6-ed6a-4565-8065-e729eb0f2650",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 1314,
        "char_end": 1404,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 88120,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 93599,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0001 - A.I. Backlash Turns Violent _ Ka_20260421-175353_8eb5f9d2.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:ae9b59bd92bcf8ca",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "I think you and I both over the past few months have seen public sentiment really begin to turn against AI. And this week, unfortunately, we saw that sentiment spill over into violence.",
        "episode_id": "25d702f6-ed6a-4565-8065-e729eb0f2650",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 3393,
        "char_end": 3578,
